    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Rigid, boxlike containers, usually large and often reinforced, for packing clothing and other personal gear or articles for travel or storage.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
